proj_get_dependencies.Rd

Get package dependencies from the DESCRIPTION file.

Usage

get_proj_dependencies()

proj_get_dependencies()

Value

A character vector of package names.

Functions

  • get_proj_dependencies(): Deprecated function. Use proj_get_dependencies() instead.
